  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>The gods of the forge are patrons of artisans who work with metal, from a humble blacksmith who keeps a village in horseshoes and plow blades to the mighty elf artisan whose diamond-tipped arrows of mithral have felled demon lords. The gods of the forge teach that, with patience and hard work, even the most intractable metal can be transformed from a lump of ore to a beautifully wrought object. Clerics of these deities search for objects lost to the forces of darkness, liberate mines overrun by orcs, and uncover rare and wondrous materials necessary to create potent magic items. Followers of these gods take great pride in their work, and they are willing to craft and use heavy armor and powerful weapons to protect them. Deities of this domain include Gond, Reorx, Onatar, Moradin, Hephaestus, and Goibhniu.</p>\n<h3>Forge Domain Spells</h3>\n<table>\n<thead style=\"text-shadow:1px 1px var(--color-shadow-dark);border-bottom:1px solid var(--color-border-dark)\">\n<tr>\n<td>Cleric Level</td>\n<td>Spells</td>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td>1st</td>\n<td>@Compendium[5e-complete.5e-spells.Cb2HnkHTxKDkI1f0]{Identify}, @Compendium[5e-complete.5e-spells.V26M46ELOjVDI2jq]{Searing Smite}</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>3rd</td>\n<td>@Compendium[5e-complete.5e-spells.42MD8VjwHZHYGiCk]{Heat Metal}, @Compendium[5e-complete.5e-spells.6Wy3kcKkuUadyapw]{Magic Weapon}</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>5th</td>\n<td>@Compendium[5e-complete.5e-spells.fEjWft78oYHZIlqe]{Elemental Weapon}, @Compendium[5e-complete.5e-spells.mosnEaBOzuz4bT8y]{Protection from Energy}</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>7th</td>\n<td>@Compendium[5e-complete.5e-spells.YYlHmGQ9fUr8YGQT]{Fabricate}, @Compendium[5e-complete.5e-spells.PDJgiO07Vyb86jd5]{Wall of Fire}</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>9th</td>\n<td>@Compendium[5e-complete.5e-spells.RvD26Eo9FIwlDxj7]{Animate Objects}, @Compendium[5e-complete.5e-spells.K7igBJaVcaIJqerK]{Creation}</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<h3>Forge Domain Features</h3>\n<p>1st Level: @Compendium[5e-complete.5e-class-features.Kse0fV2u5XGj6rrK]{Bonus Proficiencies}, @Compendium[5e-complete.5e-class-features.fmPgM8XsxKPJw7tT]{Blessing of the Forge}</p>\n<p>2nd Level: @Compendium[5e-complete.5e-class-features.sBhcDN40j2LlEnUB]{Channel Divinity: Artisan's Blessing}</p>\n<p>6th Level: @Compendium[5e-complete.5e-class-features.GyP0oRwLh8sZGZpC]{Soul of the Forge}</p>\n<p>8th Level: @Compendium[5e-complete.5e-class-features.gsVLtZzuHGIjaE5H]{Divine Strike}</p>\n<p>17th Level: @Compendium[5e-complete.5e-class-features.rs1PRurMGo8e71zW]{Saint of Forge and Fire}</p>",
